    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"meaning\" stuff feels so forced. Like people just invent it to hide from the fact that we’re just biological accidents. If there’s really nothing there, then chasing \"growth\" or \"connection\" is just a distraction from the void, isn't it? It doesn't actually make the emptiness go away.",
